      • addConfigurableActions

        void addConfigurableActions(java.lang.String panelid,
                            java.lang.Object source,
                            javax.swing.JComponent component)
        Bind the controller of the ConfigurableActions of the panel 'panelid' to the component 'component'.
        Parameters:
        panelid - Identifier of the panel from which we want to obtain the actions.
        source - Component that will be passed to the actions when they are executed, usually the instance of the panel they are associated with.
        component - Component to which we want to bind the ConfiguraActions controller.
